text: Devonport High School for Boys is a grammar school in Plymouth, England. It is also known as DHSB. DHSB is open to only those who pass the 11+ test for those aged 9-11 years. DHSB is a boy's only school, apart from sixth form, where the gender is mixed for the last 2 years of education. ==References== Category:Organisations based in Plymouth, Devon Category:Grammar schools in England
title: Devonport High School for Boys
